# Kernel out-of-tree module build artifacts
*.o
*.o.d
*.o.cmd
*.ko
*.ko.cmd
*.mod
*.mod.c
*.mod.cmd
.*.cmd
modules.order
Module.symvers
artifacts/
work/
!data/ask-userspace/libcli/
fmc_config_data.c

# accel-ppp-ng/ is a build-time clone created by bin/ci-build-accel-ppp.sh
# (clones accel-ppp/accel-ppp-ng @ commit 3e30d9b to build daemon + ipoe
# .kmods on ARM64, since the upstream VyOS arm64 mirror does not provide
# accel-ppp-ng .debs). The directory is root-owned, has its own .git, and
# is regenerated on every CI / local-build.sh run — so it must NOT be
# committed into this repo.
accel-ppp-ng/

# ASK userspace build artifacts (autotools, regenerated by ci-build-ask-userspace.sh / local builds)
